==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Instantly
<hw>In"stant*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Without the least delay or interval; at once; immediately.</def>
<rj><au>Macaulay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>With urgency or importunity; earnestly;
pressingly.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧They besought him <xex>instantly</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Luke vii. 4.</au></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Directly; immediately; at once. See
<er>Directly</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Instar</ent>⟦br⟧
